# RockEncantech

E-commerce catalog challenge with Laravel backend and React frontend.

## Current status
- Backend API completed
- Frontend in progress

## Backend stack
- Laravel
- MySQL
- Laravel Sanctum
- Service + Repository pattern

## Implemented endpoints
- GET /api/products
- GET /api/products/{id}
- GET /api/categories
- POST /api/register
- POST /api/login
- Protected product create/update/delete

## Run backend locally
```bash
cd backend
composer install
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
php artisan migrate:fresh --seed
php artisan serve